Accept: {{json}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get recent activities with limit
# Lấy hoạt động gần đây với limit
GET {{base}}/api/dashboard/recent?limit=5
Accept: {{json}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get recent activities with invalid limit
